Rootless GoboLinux is a way to install GoboLinux environment
in unprivileged user under unixlike operating systems.

You can read about it [here](http://gobolinux.org/?page=rootless)

An installer [is available](http://github.com/thoughtsofcode/GoboRootless_Installer).

It is also possible to install Rootless GoboLinux in the
[Cygwin environment under Microsoft Windows](Rootless on Cygwin).
